comments: Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a wide screening position in the path of Matthews (MIL) and delivers marginal contact during the pick that does not affect his ability to defend.
Butler (MIA) places a hand on Antetokounmpo's (MIL) back and makes marginal contact in transition that does not affect his SQBR.
Adebayo (MIA) swipes down and avoids making contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm during his shooting motion, and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Portis (MIL) initiates marginal contact with Adebayo (MIA) during the pick.
Butler (MIA) swipes down and makes contact to the arm of Antetokounmpo (MIL) during the pass.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact with Matthews (MIL) as he sets the screen.
Holiday (MIL) and Tucker (MIA) make incidental contact during the pick.
At the start of the drive, Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes marginal contact to Vincent's (MIA) arm that does not affect his ability to defend.
Tucker (MIA) extends his hand and makes marginal contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) front during his driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) and Matthews (MIL) make incidental contact during the rebound.
Portis (MIL) legally defends Herro (MIA) on the perimeter and deflects the ball.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) and Butler (MIA) arrive at the ball simultaneously during the inbound pass and the body contact that occurs is incidental.
Butler (MIA) receives the pass and lands on two feet prior to falling to the ground.
Before the held ball, Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes marginal contact to the arm of Butler (MIA) as he attempts to tie up the ball.
Holiday (MIL) goes to but not through Vincent (MIA) when the marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt. Vincent's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
